			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65403695" name="comment_link_65403695" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23702019&amp;cid=65403695" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65403695)" >Re:Are we surprised yet?</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65403695" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65403695); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
